725
01:13:05,712 --> 01:13:07,594
[SPEAKER_12]: and creating some down below as well.

726
01:13:10,276 --> 01:13:23,306
[SPEAKER_12]: As we shift to building on Edgerley Field primarily, in terms of this addition that could be connected down below or up above with some type of bridge or connection down below the surface,

727
01:13:25,187 --> 01:13:43,995
[SPEAKER_12]: If we're building off the entirety of the existing footprint, which is really what Edge really offers as an option, that starts to become the scenarios that are least impactful to education, because it means that we can build a majority of new construction without impacting what's going on down here, other than site construction access.

728
01:13:44,015 --> 01:13:48,096
[SPEAKER_12]: There's still going to be trucks that are accessing up the site and building things here.

729
01:13:48,176 --> 01:13:51,338
