731
01:13:54,499 --> 01:14:14,712
[SPEAKER_12]: But in terms of having to use modular classrooms to alleviate or compensate for taking down some of the existing wings, this C3.3 option is one of the ones that we're not projecting would require any modular classrooms as part of the construction activity, which is why you see the zero down here.

