769
01:18:40,952 --> 01:19:02,615
[SPEAKER_12]: sure yeah and again i know i sound like a broken record but i'm happy to modify things as we go forward i didn't intend for everything to be right going through here on the first pass the the thought process there was the fact that once we get up to like those seven or eight story buildings that maintenance just becomes inherently more challenging just because we have to we have to have more

770
