773
01:19:16,239 --> 01:19:32,323
[SPEAKER_12]: We can certainly shift it from a zero to a two, potentially, as a modification, just to make it more reflective of the fact that it's not horrible, it's just less than ideal as if you can potentially achieve that in a three or four-story building, for instance.

774
01:19:37,027 --> 01:19:42,313
