01:35:22,095 --> 01:35:37,785
[SPEAKER_12]: The reason why it is less expensive than renovating the existing pool, and that's where I was getting hung up on, is the complexity of the fact that the existing pool by itself is sort of connected in with a lot of other square footage that's there that would have to be renovated at the same time.

943
